snippet: A victory Tuesday night would give Rutgers Coach C. Vivian Stringer her 900th career win. But she is more focused on leading her team to the N.C.A.A. tournament.
abstract: Rutgers women's basketball coach C Vivian Stringer is one victory short of her 900th career win, but she remains completely focused on leading her team to the NCAA tournament.
lead_paragraph: A victory Tuesday night would give Rutgers Coach C. Vivian Stringer her 900th career win. But she is more focused on leading her team to the N.C.A.A. tournament.
